        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "petrochemical company"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "About The Client",
        "The company leading Saudi Arabian petrochemical company, established as a joint venture. It operates one of the largest integrated refining and petrochemical complexes in the Middle East, producing a wide range of refined hydrocarbons and petrochemical products used globally across plastics, fuels, packaging, detergents, automotive components, and more."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Fragmented HR Policy Management and Reactive Decision-Making"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Key Business Areas Impacted Included:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Employee experience and confidence"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "HR operational efficiency"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Policy governance and compliance"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "It manages a large workforce operating within a highly regulated environment. While HR policies were documented and accessible, the organization struggled to manage policy understanding, feedback, and updates in a structured and scalable way.",
        "This company manages a large workforce operating within a highly regulated environment. While HR policies were documented and accessible, the organization struggled to manage policy understanding, feedback, and updates in a structured and scalable way.",
        "As a result, HR teams spent a significant amount of time handling repetitive, low-value tasks instead of focusing on strategic initiatives.",
        "Repeated questions and unclear policies reduced employee trust and clarity.",
        "Manual handling of queries, feedback, and updates consumed excessive HR time.",
        "Informal feedback, delayed approvals, and manual change tracking increased governance"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
